WEBVTT

00:04:54.664 --> 00:05:00.064
where we work with TATA Trust, and we
train women in rural Indian villages.

00:05:00.064 --> 00:05:04.064
We've been doing it across a 
100,000 villages in 12 states

00:05:04.064 --> 00:05:06.864
and we've trained millions of women.

00:05:06.864 --> 00:05:10.454
(Applause)

00:05:10.454 --> 00:05:14.644
SRK: What do you think we're going to leave
for our children and grandchildren?

00:05:14.644 --> 00:05:18.354
What is the future of technology 
according to you?

00:05:18.354 --> 00:05:22.764
SP: It's very exciting. Today we use 
computers like we use smartphones.

00:05:22.764 --> 00:05:26.764
But if you fast-forward many 
years from now, I think,

00:05:26.764 --> 00:05:30.764
computing and the world's 
knowledge will be there with you